== 製作 ==
編劇G·O·帕森斯（{{lang|en|G. O. Parsons}}）對自己的電影生涯並不滿意，於是為了取得更進一步的成功而寫了名為《沃利的遊樂園》（{{lang|en|Wally's Wonderland}}）的短篇劇本。他將該劇本放到{{le|Blood List|Blood List}}上，力求將其拍成長片。該劇本在網站上得到了特別報導，並引起了[[尼可拉斯·凱吉|尼可拉斯·凱吉]]的注意，後者同意製作並出演電影。<ref name="Yahoo!_Review">{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/review-horror-comedy-willys-wonderland-154929634.html|title=Review: Horror-comedy 'Willy's Wonderland' isn't nearly wacky enough to deserve Nicolas Cage|last=Murray|first=Noel|work=[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]|date=2021-02-12|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802095400/https://news.yahoo.com/review-horror-comedy-willys-wonderland-154929634.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{le|銀幕媒體影業|Screen Media Films}}於2019年10月宣布，經[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]證實，主演凱吉與JD娛樂（{{lang|en|JD Entertainment}}）的製片人傑瑞米·戴維斯（{{lang|en|Jeremy Davis}}）和蘭達法爾娛樂（{{lang|en|Landafar Entertainment}}）的{{le|格蘭特·克萊默|Grant Cramer}}都將擔任監製，凱吉的土星影業（{{lang|en|Saturn Films}}）也將參與製作。<ref name="tosta" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Nicolas Cage to Star in Twisted Theme Park Thriller 'Wally's Wonderland' {{!}} Hollywood Reporter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/nicolas-cage-star-wallys-wonderland-1251086#:~:text=Nicolas%20Cage%20is%20set%20to,Parsons.|access-date=2020-12-05|website=www.hollywoodreporter.com|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129053011/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/nicolas-cage-star-wallys-wonderland-1251086#:~:text=Nicolas%20Cage%20is%20set%20to,Parsons.|dead-url=no}}</ref>曾執導《{{le|第三顆釘子|The Third Nail}}》（2008年）的凱文·路易士（{{lang|en|Kevin Lewis}}）被聘來擔任導演。2020年2月，{{le|艾蜜莉·托斯塔|Emily Tosta}}、{{le|貝絲·格蘭特|Beth Grant}}、{{le|瑞克·萊茲|Ric Reitz}}、克里斯·華納（{{lang|en|Chris Warner}}）及[[凱莉·考恩|凱莉·考恩]]加入演出陣容。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/party-five-emily-tosta-joins-nicolas-cage-wallys-wonderland-1202851916/|title=‘Party Of Five’ Star Emily Tosta Joins Nicolas Cage In Genre Thriller ‘Wally’s Wonderland’|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-02-05|accessdate=2020-03-03|first=Andreas|last=Wiseman|archive-date=2020-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408021657/https://deadline.com/2020/02/party-five-emily-tosta-joins-nicolas-cage-wallys-wonderland-1202851916/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後，電影更名為《弒樂園》（{{lang|en|Willy's Wonderland}}）<ref name="EW(2020-10-30)">{{cite news|url=https://ew.com/movies/willys-wonderland-trailer-nicolas-cage/|title=Watch Nicolas Cage battle giant animatronic animals in Willy's Wonderland teaser|last=Collis|first=Clark|work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2020-10-30|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115202309/https://ew.com/movies/willys-wonderland-trailer-nicolas-cage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

